Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上的波涛声 比平时更加清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炫目的月光充满了天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那月光如此温暖地 拥抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 若能尽情享受世界给我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 新威尼斯的秋天快要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很快就要迎来寒冬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爱丽丝先行成为正式领航员了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的共同练习已经变成了与蓝华两个人的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华啊 开始变冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有两个人的共同练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是让人想起我们刚刚相识的情形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在说完全不寂寞是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是非常值得高兴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们也不能输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一起为了成为正式领航员努力吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能再跟你一起共同练习了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直努力着 梦想着这一天的到来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你晋级为正式领航员 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…我就知道灯里会这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一件事想跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.79,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那片 蔚蓝的大海与风…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 蓝华她晋级为正式领航员了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是个好消息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称号是Rozen Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蔷薇女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定下来是那个了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃一直都在烦恼这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候进行蓝华的晋级考试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为蓝华不仅仅是要成为正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还要背负整个姬屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果是蓝华的话一定不会有问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢 我还有一个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑塔·露琪亚附近要开一家姬屋的分店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(265,440)\fs20}Santa Lucia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华要到那里担任分店长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她说以后会变得很忙很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是件值得高兴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华却哭得很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天将对你进行正式领航员晋级考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在好紧张哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我终于要面对晋级考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为实在紧张得睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以虽然是晚上 我还是出去练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 终于等到这一天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长 谢谢你陪我出来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 就跟平时练习一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了 不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚从中学的同学会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就弄丢钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明牢牢系在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 鬓子你这么晚在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…是我的正式领航员晋级考试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷最近也要进行晋级考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常了解鬓子你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 晓 我找到你的钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？在哪找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掉在店里的洗手间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…居然在那种怎么都不可能掉的地方掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭钱包 你给我去厕所睡觉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 晓 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？灯里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么晚还在练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓子啊 考试加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望天气不要变坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得努力睡一觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 远方的天空很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午应该就放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晋级考试…不如延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是个重要的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新选一个天气好的日子再考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直等着这一天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是艾莉西亚前辈决定给我考试的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天对于我来说 已经很重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是下午也一直下的话就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备工作都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热水袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真体贴的服务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位和毯子都暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里到大运河之间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从任何一个地方都能遥望大钟楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 雨过天晴之后我最推荐的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这条小路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是赛艇的选手先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的船桨都是自己做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的路要由自己来闯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话 就会留下遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年我要夺冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤尾舟要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于到了大运河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(515,440)\fs20}Canal Grande
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新威尼斯的版图上画出一个倒S型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大运河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人您冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是横跨大运河的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里亚托桥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ponte di Rialto
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是水上通行之人与桥上眺望之人邂逅的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓 她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 伍迪 我们按计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hurray～ hurray～ 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}hurray～ hurray～ 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}加油啊 灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晓先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚小姐也要加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快给我下来 小心掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤尾舟要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕阳西下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣马可广场和被称为Lagoon的泻湖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不断变换着色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像被温暖的颜色所环抱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在其中不断被治愈一样不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 操纵凤尾舟的技巧和导游词都很熟练了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还能感觉到灯里独特的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…非常重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 这条水路…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 平时是禁止新人进入的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在我们可以进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着水路尽头的 灯里的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前任何一条水路都要窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还有这样的水路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人不可思议地 感觉不到慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三人总是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从船桨传达到指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深邃而静谧的 水的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与大家度过的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撑着现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有力地推动着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤尾舟要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 这次的凤尾舟之旅太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠静而恬然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像凤尾舟与海水融合在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这是最后的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始的路线由灯里你来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为怎样的正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要由灯里自己来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为怎样的正式领航员吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事物即将有所转变之时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都踏上了属于自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像相互催发着对方的变化一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连锁重叠起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切 从最初都已经被命运所决定一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要成为的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是像祖母那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像艾莉西亚前辈这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像亚利亚公司一样的领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你来到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的世界就翻开了新的一页
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都开始闪烁着迷人的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人施展了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像温柔地环抱着AQUA的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延伸到无尽远方的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空与大海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的海蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海蓝…宝石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深邃的…蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你晋级成为正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 我是正式领航员了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直一直…都憧憬着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从踏足这颗星球那一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件重要的事情要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断变换的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恬静温馨的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.56,0:24:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个人的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我将启程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.65,0:24:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.91,0:24:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 崭新的开端…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.58,0:24:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:57.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:07.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:17.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:28.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:33.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:40.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:47.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:57.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.45,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:11.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:19.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
