Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:07.14,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:17.27,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.67,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:28.40,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:33.12,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:40.24,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:47.18,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 崭露头角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.54,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永远地 充满
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:57.18,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让人陶醉的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.45,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:11.17,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}每个温暖的 日子往复着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:19.59,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不经意间 从那远方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.29,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}来到我身边
