Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:17.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あこがれ目覚めるの 朝に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}始まる
